erved brightness\ntemperature and/or the assumption of equipartition may lead to large scatter or\nsystematic errors in the derived values.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2006 21:27:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
