 and its antiwall partner (at strong coupling in the bulk\ntheory) are stabilized at the opposite sides of the cylinder.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2006 20:12:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 30 Apr 2006 18:46:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 5 Aug 2006 16:16:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-05-27"}
