ult will be\ndeveloped here. They confirm Lorentz-Fitzgerald's contraction and lend support\nof the existence of a preferred aether frame.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Mar 2006 14:47:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Aug 2008 13:43:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 8 Mar 2010 17:11:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-03-09"}
